			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Not sure how a spell posting turns into a PvP arguement but anyway I'll play along.  First of all let me say that my primary char is a necro.  The winner in PvP is almost always determined by the exp of the fighter.  In other words, THERE IS NO HARD AND FAST RULE REGARDING WHICH CLASS IS BETTER IN PVP.<BR>
<BR>
Secondly, I am quite surprised that the enchanter has not yet been mentioned.  A well played lvl50 enc will beat any other lvl50 class in PvP.  In fact, the enc will usually kill you before you even can cast a spell.  <BR>
<BR>
Finally, I cant help but comment to Ilnati in response to your battle w/ a lvl40 wizzie.  I have no doubts that a well played lvl40 wiz could kill a lvl42 necro, BUT wizzies do not get Ice Comet until lvl49 so he killed you with something else.  <BR>
<BR>
All that said...PLEASE PEOPLE TRY TO POST INFO ON THE SUBJECT AT HAND.  IF YOU WISH TO ARGUE PVP PLAY GO DO IT ON ONE OF THE CHAT BOARDS!
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
